        "# ----- Reuse the BAAI/bge-m3 embedder already loaded as `embedder` -----\n",
        "# Some metrics (response_relevancy) need embeddings. We wrap the in-memory\n",
        "# SentenceTransformer with the LangChain Embeddings interface so RAGAS can\n",
